<eesti>Kohtusse kaebamine </eesti>
<inglise>Appeal in court </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Ettev&otilde;tjal on &otilde;igus Tehnilise J&auml;relevalve Inspektsiooni v&otilde;i Energiaturu Inspektsiooni ametniku ettekirjutuse v&otilde;i muu toiminguga mitten&otilde;ustumisel esitada kaebus halduskohtusse, s&otilde;ltumata k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahvis 33 nimetatud kaebuse varasemast esitamisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An undertaking who disagrees with a precept issued or procedure implemented by an official of the Technical Inspectorate or Energy Market Inspectorate has the right to file an appeal with an administrative court, regardless of the previous filing of a complaint specified in &sect; 33 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaebuse esitamine kohtusse ei v&otilde;ta ettev&otilde;tjalt kohustust t&auml;ita Tehnilise J&auml;relevalve Inspektsiooni v&otilde;i Energiaturu Inspektsiooni ametniku ettekirjutust seni, kuni kohus tunnistab selle kas osaliselt v&otilde;i t&auml;ielikult seadusevastaseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The filing of an appeal with a court does not relieve an undertaking of the duty to comply with a precept issued by an official of the Technical Inspectorate or Energy Market Inspectorate until the court declares such precept to be partially or wholly unlawful. </inglise>
